<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>進階查詢</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="advanced-search.css">
</head>
<body>
    <h1>進階查詢</h1>

    <table id="advancedSearchTable">
        <tr>
            <th>ID</th>
            <th>小孩排序</th>
            <th>姓名</th>
            <th>出生年月日</th>
            <th>血型</th>
            <th>MORE</th>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>000740077</td>
            <td>1</td>
            <td>蔡平平(男)</td>
            <td>110/03/11</td>
            <td>A</td>
            <td>
                <span class="toggleContent">&#9656;</span>
                <div class="moreContent" style="display: none;">
                    <p>嬰兒於早晨7:30順利出生，體重3.3公斤，身長50公分，經過初步檢查，呼吸順暢，哭聲強烈，皮膚呈自然紅潤，無異常情況。APGAR評分為9分，身體各項指標穩定。母親情況良好，順利經歷陰道分娩，無出血等併發症，正在接受常規監測與護理。父母情緒激動，初次抱起寶寶時表現出極大的喜悅與幸福，醫護人員也積極提供必要的育兒指導，確保母嬰安全。</p>
                </div>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>

    <nav>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="/about">返回查詢結果</a></li>
            <li><a href="/steps">步數統計</a></li>
            <li><a href="/scores">測驗分數</a></li>
            <li><a href="/analysis">分析結果</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>

    <script>
        document.querySelectorAll('.toggleContent').forEach(toggle => {
            toggle.addEventListener('click', function() {
                const content = this.nextElementSibling;
                if (content.style.display === 'none') {
                    content.style.display = 'block';
                    this.innerHTML = '&#9662;';
                } else {
                    content.style.display = 'none';
                    this.innerHTML = '&#9656;';
                }
            });
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
